      <title>Hexo Butterfly主题配置踩坑处理(持续更新)</title>
      <link href="/posts/d739a423/"/>
      <url>/posts/d739a423/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>在hexo博客Butterfly主题中，使用各种插件、修改配置等遇到的坑及处理的过程记录</p><p>人生本来就是折腾，从一个坑跳进另一个坑。声生不息，乐此不疲~</p><hr><h2 id="配置哔哔点啥ispeak-bber线上报错不加载"><a href="#配置哔哔点啥ispeak-bber线上报错不加载" class="headerlink" title="配置哔哔点啥ispeak-bber线上报错不加载"></a>配置<a href="/bb/">哔哔</a>点啥ispeak-bber线上报错不加载</h2><p>本地<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> 绑定了「<a href="/bb/">哔哔</a>点啥」公众号 、ios快捷指令、uTools插件，测试稳的一P</p><p>近期网站上线了，把hexo部署到线上后就出现了第一个报错，<a href="/bb/">哔哔</a>动态显示出不来，控制台显示是跨域的错误</p><blockquote><p>Access to XMLHttpRequest at ‘<a href="https://cloudbase-baas-$%#@%$*-shanghai.tcb-api.tencentcloudapi.com/web?env=cloudbase-baas-$%#@%$*&#39;">https://cloudbase-baas-$%#@%$*-shanghai.tcb-api.tencentcloudapi.com/web?env=cloudbase-baas-$%#@%$*&#39;</a> from origin ‘<a href="https://www.njiii.com&/#39;">https://www.njiii.com&#39;</a> has been blocked by CORS policy: Response to preflight request doesn’t pass access control check: No ‘Access-Control-Allow-Origin’ header is present on the requested resource.</p></blockquote><p><img src="/../img/img11.jpg"></p><p>首先想到是<em>SSL</em>证书安全问题，服务器安装SSL证书后还是不行。当初使用hexo就是喜欢这个能随时随地”<a href="/bb/">哔哔</a>“的功能，这下又得折腾一下子了…那么就从配置说明重新来一遍吧，后端配置参考：<a href="https://immmmm.com/bb-by-wechat-pro/">https://immmmm.com/bb-by-wechat-pro/</a>  浅过了一遍腾讯云开发部署绑定，好，没啥问题</p><p>再从底往上翻说明的时候发现了4.进入<u>环境-安全配置</u>，将网站域名添加到“<u>WEB安全域名</u>”</p><p><img src="/../img/img12.jpg"></p><p>这里也添加了域名（格式错了，自己马虎了）…最后改成泛域名*.njiii.com，搞定！</p><h2 id="留言板信笺hexo-butterfly-envelope插件报错"><a href="#留言板信笺hexo-butterfly-envelope插件报错" class="headerlink" title="留言板信笺hexo-butterfly-envelope插件报错"></a>留言板信笺hexo-butterfly-envelope插件报错</h2><p>使用<code>akilar</code>npm插件安装方式，安装后留言板没有变化，还有Git Bash报错</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">FATAL Something<span class="string">&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>试了<code>akilar</code>大佬的第二种修改源码方式添加还是报错，猜测可能自己步骤或者代码缩进没弄好，再删掉重新添加还是报错..</p><p>经历了2个小时的报错，一顿操作修改后，突然灵光一现。把之前建站时已经添加..\comments\index.md的留言文件夹删除，然后重新Git Bash</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-butterfly-envelope --save</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000/ . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开留言板页面，果断成功！</p>]]></content>
      
      
